* Iron Raptor continued to dig around a bit in the back of Prowls neck until 
she finally felt it, the severed wire which was disconnected from Prowls 
main processor.
This would be a simple fix...if she understood this body right.

It was half her second beast mode if she knew nothing else, and she knew 
just what it could do.
Simply leaning down she removed her claw from his neck, and grabbed the back 
of Prowl's neck with her mouth, biting in a bit deep.
The acid which acted as her saliva would seep into thr wound her claw made, 
actually repairing what little damage there was in the back of Prowls head.
This is what acted as her repair system, and she just hoped that it would do 
alright with Prowl.*
